{"tid":1213725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派議員：強烈譴責政府將示威活動定性為暴動","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T02:41:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c45ec2fffda4695a1af330b223df374230ba67d","tid":1213725,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190613_20190613-102502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190613_20190613-102502.jpg&h=ced52225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多名民主派議員表示，反對政府將昨日在金鐘一帶的示威活動定性為暴動，予以強烈譴責，批評警方濫用武力。<br />\n<br />\n民主派會議召集人毛孟靜要求立法會主席梁君彥，任何牽涉二讀修訂逃犯條例草案的會議，都不應該繼續，民主派會盡力阻撓法例通過。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉說，示威活動被定性為暴動，令他想起30年前的天安門事件，指責行政長官林鄭月娥鐵石心腸，與一眾助紂為虐的建制派議員及警察都萬死不能以謝天下，形容今日的林鄭月娥就等於30年前的李鵬，呼籲市民用智慧，在合法合情的情況下做任何可以阻撓政府運作的事。<br />\n<br />\n街工梁耀忠說，有救護員告知他，昨日有警察搶走救護員的鹽水，阻止他們救治受傷的青年，批評是毫無人性，呼籲政府撤回條例。"},{"pid":"ab33b1014529a31df744cb641c7f99fbb5cba382","tid":1213725,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:30:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1123337&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1123337%26csid%3D261_341&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmiWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=b1bc1f04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1123337&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"3e6bb4a4b7e105d8113a5d9f849a379e21a88b17","tid":1213725,"uid":15121,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bf1492dbef12cc0078c6bbe3eb7982a3fe23bc","tid":1213725,"uid":79403,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:32:21.000Z","msg":"梁耀忠仲有面出嚟講嘢"},{"pid":"df7901279e5